{"tid":1018090,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]找番條數 講下點樣切野開雞同埋整梅菜扣肉","createTime":"2019-02-12T03:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T00:11:08.000Z","uid":28007,"like":141,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8df5eeedb8d228fee37823843e7f12aa341ca0","tid":1018090,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"大家好 又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先多得咁多位巴絲打既支持 上個post反應先會咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁上次個post都好多人會問有關切野既問題<br />\n例如切到尾要點做 啲手既擺位要點樣等等<br />\n咁細佬我就拍左條片講解交流下既<br />\n<br />\n事關用文字表達都幾麻煩同埋會唔清楚 所以段片我都會聲音導航<br />\n但係我把聲就死鬼老牛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係其實原來拍片講野都幾緊張 會有咬字唔清楚 講錯野要cut片既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁依一段都會有字幕 因為都幾重要<br />\n希望咁多位可以體諒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/taJ52pzPhr4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtaJ52pzPhr4&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIunyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=f261cecc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/taJ52pzPhr4</a><br />\n<br />\n總括黎講 切到尾會平衡點無左 所以會放平黎片<br />\n切野我建議切矮嗰邊 <br />\n可以想象係把刀推緊隻手黎切<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\n慢啲無所謂 最緊要安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就會講解下點樣係屋企開雞<br />\n話曬新年流流<br />\n無隻雞睇下檔點得<br />\n咁都係嗰講 開雞係比較危險<br />\n用家用刀開更加要小心<br />\n同埋都會傷把刀<br />\n大家要自行衝量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我會出聲講下有咩要注意<br />\n如果介意我把聲 同樣都係 真係唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係依段就無字幕既<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Pm3eSBKu9ps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPm3eSBKu9ps&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIunyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=e91fecd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Pm3eSBKu9ps</a><br />\n<br />\n話說鋪頭之前出左腩肉餐<br />\n我見難得就攞左一舊仔去整梅菜扣肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係都幾唔老例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新年邊有人食梅菜<br />\n咁大家可以睇完就算 千其唔好團年飯嗰陣整比屋企人食<br />\n<br />\n咁用到既材料會有腩肉（約一磅）<br />\n甜梅菜（隨心）<br />\n乾蔥（少許）<br />\n柱侯醬<br />\n海鮮醬<br />\n豪油<br />\n重有最為緊要既南乳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實扣肉做法簡單 只係多步驟<br />\n首先腩肉出水8成熟左右再過冷河<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkmRxLf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkmRxLf.png&h=45bce108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等佢乾左就撚少許老抽落面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ErhpSLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErhpSLk.png&h=00e9d525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再攞左炸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bQWqCb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbQWqCb4.png&h=e05c6f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後梅菜連乾蔥爆香<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVd8zYP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVd8zYP.png&h=a44e3f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再撈番上述既醬汁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OxhtiU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OxhtiU.png&h=da515c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海鮮醬 柱侯醬 豪油 南乳既比例大概係3:0.5:1:1 <br />\n<br />\n我唔直接講份量既原因好簡單 <br />\n咁樣整出黎既野食照跟食譜係唔會有意思<br />\n食物就係人人都整出黎都有唔同 先有樂趣<br />\n至少我唔希望人人都跟足我既份量黎做<br />\n<br />\n然後再加番多啲糖 少少鹽同雞粉<br />\n<br />\n最後就將腩肉切片 再撈下啲醬汁 然後擺碟 梅菜放面腩肉放底咁蒸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wMJ8i0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wMJ8i0.png&h=4d7f32e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒸一個鐘就食得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWNmaxr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWNmaxr.png&h=7620960e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hgmUY7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hgmUY7.png&h=e689040a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果想再好味啲就放最少4-5個鐘 然後番蒸半個蒸<br />\n<br />\n咁個人少建議就係 腩肉切片厚身啲先有口感<br />\n慢慢試下味 新手唔好一次過落太多<br />\n仲有煮南乳好易燶 可以最後先落<br />\n<br />\n咁最後當晚我仲炒左碟炒麵食 只係我朋友佢話拍完曝光太勁 用唔到段片<br />\n<br />\n今日就差唔多 都係嗰句 歡迎咁多位交流 希望大家可以搵到煮野食既樂趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於挑機嗰啲 問我其他問題嗰啲 建議我整其他野食嗰啲 我遲啲一定會完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後附上當晚我地食既晚餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PQZGEp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PQZGEp.png&h=5dd56881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都幾on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n片就一早拍好<br />\n篇野都一早整好<br />\n上字幕年30晚搞到7788<br />\n只係唔記得左開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n團年飯大家都食完好耐 但係都希望今個post可以令大家識多樣野<br />\n<br />\n多謝你睇到依到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4e4dce859dc0d4eb72a9cdc9a20d5ff888d656","tid":1018090,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbaa91c08083931957fe6e52f56d064e23cf8da","tid":1018090,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"老鐵66666"},{"pid":"2fbb90b39f9d32a6977b87aa2ce4bbc9a2f3e86c","tid":1018090,"uid":112645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"f3619903c093921c1517e9c6c7f921d5408af711","tid":1018090,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea4e4dce859dc0d4eb72a9cdc9a20d5ff888d656","tid":1018090,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a9c81923a5f7f158e97e5975fa7ed2f5bc4b2c","tid":1018090,