hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實拍片係因為上個post好多人問我<br />\n我都好難用文字圖片都講解點切野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話曬都危險<br />\n<br />\n好多謝巴打支持 <br />\n雖然個post沉左 但係我會繼續開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea6535ff1af4fde262f53447a7829314bd517b9","tid":1018090,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"想問炒飯 個飯唔知係好濕定太熟 淋bat bat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經用隔夜飯炒有時都係咁 已經可以炒到佢一粒粒 但食落冇咩口感<br />\n炒飯嘅飯係咪要超少水煮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bd8c9c74cc2300c797f57d5ecd92345471b333","tid":1018090,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:47:15.000Z","msg":"扣肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d6e70d545958022a9f4b26260a3e6cb09f7b45","tid":1018090,"uid":28007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ea6535ff1af4fde262f53447a7829314bd517b9","tid":1018090,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"想問炒飯 個飯唔知係好濕定太熟 淋bat bat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經用隔夜飯炒有時都係咁 已經可以炒到佢一粒粒 但食落冇咩口感<br />\n炒飯嘅飯係咪要超少水煮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"飯太淋姐係爛飯<br />\n水同米既比例錯左<br />\n爛飯炒飯真係神仙都難救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用隔夜飯炒飯唔代表一定掂<br />\n想口感好啲 由煲飯嗰下開始決定左<br />\n<br />\n我建議煲飯嗰陣落少啲水 <br />\n咁煲出黎既飯唔使等隔夜<br />\n即用都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋炒飯 最好要步驟連貫<br />\n事關炒飯炒太耐都會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗屋企炒 頂盡5-7分鐘就要起鑊<br />\n<br />\n同埋炒飯唔使落水 <br />\n落多啲啲油就得<img src=\"/a